{"tid":2121271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"破壞區議員橫額兼於警長臉上鎅「交叉」 七旬翁罪成囚兩年 蘇文隆:裁判法院條例最高只能判處兩年 否則必定判處更高刑期","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T17:19:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ce65bdf996b6cdf5033c31b85d50a944f0d827","tid":2121271,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/6VBLHW4ZTRW7Z5XSGBZBFHS36M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2F6VBLHW4ZTRW7Z5XSGBZBFHS36M%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=e4c255df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2F6VBLHW4ZTRW7Z5XSGBZBFHS36M%2F&h=2caf20ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/6VBLHW4ZTRW7Z5XSGBZBFHS36M/</a><br />\n<br />\n七旬翁疑因村屋租務糾紛，去年涉三度鎅爛前民建聯區議員的選舉橫額，被捕時更以刀片在拘捕他的警長右臉上「打交叉」。老翁被控三項刑事毀壞及一項傷人罪，今於粉嶺裁判法院被裁定罪名成立。<strong><span class=\"red\">主任裁判官蘇文隆形容被告出手殘忍，險令警長致盲，判被告監禁兩年。蘇官又謂，基於裁判法院相關條例規限下，最高只能判處兩年監禁，否則必定判處更高刑期。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5ead8a7dc771c98d18c4f597ecf0750155540dd7","tid":2121271,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85ea5cfc11b26c575838b9947caea6211ea1fac","tid":2121271,"uid":151313,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"好似係藍絲黎既？"},{"pid":"f5dd4ec0bb89a0459380862e536a3f8fab5ab5f7","tid":2121271,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29ade88b8f5ec575b2